  "name": "RPlog_Three_Point_Landing",
  "title": "Crash-Landing on Dathomir",
  "summary": "A battle-damaged Marine shuttle limps down onto the forested slopes of Dathomir, its engines failing a hundred meters up and skidding to a rough landing among ancient trees. Lieutenant Wrista Ipex rallies her marines -- the medic Leyanne, the battered pilot Sergeant Wilks, and the dangling, cursing Vengan -- to evacuate, take a head count, and strip the wreck of sensors, comms, and salvageable gear while strange wildlife shrieks in the distance. When a flaming X-Wing screams overhead and crashes nearby, Wrista and Leyanne set out through purbole-infested jungle, Wrista using xenobiology tricks to ward off the territorial primates, to reach the downed pilot. At the crash site they find the fighter pilot Raxis 'Spider' standing guard over his injured, sleeping comrade Hotwire beneath a propped-up wing. After a cautious peaceful approach, recognition and relief follow, and the group prepares to move the wounded Hotwire back to the marines' camp while Wrista erases their tracks behind them.",
